@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Company
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Quản Lý Công Ty

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant CompanyService as "Company\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Công Ty ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Công ty của tôi"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: GET /api/companies?recruiterId={id}
CompanyService -> Database: Query cong_ty
Database --> CompanyService: Return list
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Companies list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị danh sách

== Tạo Công Ty ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Tạo công ty"
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Nhập: tên, địa chỉ, mã thuế, logo
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/companies\n(tenCongTy, diaChi, maSoThue, logoUrl)
CompanyService -> Database: Create cong_ty
Database --> CompanyService: Return companyId
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Created
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Tạo công ty

== Xem Chi Tiết ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click vào công ty
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: GET /api/companies/{companyId}
CompanyService -> Database: Get company info
Database --> CompanyService: Details
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Full info
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị chi tiết

== Thêm Ngành Nghề ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Thêm ngành"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: GET /api/industries
CompanyService -> Database: Get all industries
Database --> CompanyService: Industries list
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: List
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show dropdown

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Chọn ngành
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: POST /api/companies/{companyId}/industries\n(nganhId)
CompanyService -> Database: Create ct_cty_nganh
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Added
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Thêm ngành thành công

== Cập Nhật Công Ty ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Sửa"
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Nhập dữ liệu mới
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: PUT /api/companies/{companyId}
CompanyService -> Database: Update cong_ty
Database --> CompanyService: OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: Updated
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Cập nhật thành công

@enduml
